<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (bnḥbk nsjd lyk .. ạ̹nt fạdynạ
 bnḥbk nrfʿ lyk .. kl ạ̉gẖạnynạ
 bnḥbk ạ̹nt lynạ .. kl mạ lynạ
 bnḥbk yạlly sạkn .. fy ạ̉wạnynạ)2
 1- yạ sạkn jwh qlwbnạ .. ʿynynạ bttrjạk
 msẖ mmkn qlb hysẖbʿ .. yạ yswʿ ạ̹lạ bmrậk
 sbb frḥ qlwbnạ .. ạ̹nnạ jnbyk
 wạlly yskn fy strk .. ylqy̱ ḥmạyth fyk
 2- qlbk mlyạn bạlrḥmẗ .. wạlkẖyr llmw̉mnyn
 wbtgẖmrnạ bạlnʿmẗ .. wbdmk mstwryn
 sbb rạḥẗ qlwbnạ .. ạ̹nnạ fy ạydyk
 wạlly yậmn bṣlybk .. ylqy̱ ḍmạnh fyk</lyrics>
